title: Svenja Huth: Players 'live for these type of games' vs Real Madrid
snippet: — VfL Wolfsburg Frauen (@VfL_Frauen) December 8, 2025 · Wolfsburg returned from the international break with a win but their game against Real Madrid on Tuesday is their biggest of the season so far. “It wasn’t easy for the team to get back into the normal rhythm again after only one training session together,” said Wolfsburg’s Svenja Huth.
